2025-12-11T12:07:43.261+09:00  INFO 1129209 --- [kompile-sample] [nio-8085-exec-6] a.k.a.w.c.DocumentManagementController   :   Chunk 4235 preview: '“So I’m on my way to rescue my dad.'
